  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Main] Trigger \uFF1CDe-DigivoLv.e 1\uFF1E on 1 of your
    opponent's Digimon. (Trash a card from the top of one of your opponent's Digimon.
    If it has no digivolution cards\uFF0C or becomes a level 3 Digimon\uFF0C you
    can't trash any more cards.) Then\uFF0C if that Digimon's play cost is 4 or less\uFF0C
    delete it."
